# **Go Logs --- Minimal CLI Log Editor**

**Database-agnostic â€¢ In-memory demo â€¢ Clean package design**

A tiny, menu-driven **CLI application** for creating, viewing, editing,
and deleting log records. The architecture is intentionally simple: the
`logs` package interacts only with an abstract database layer that
exposes `Get`, `Create`, `Patch`, and `Delete`.

The included `database` package provides a **lightweight in-memory
store** so the app runs out-of-the-box.

> **Note:** The app has **no persistence by default**.\
> Logs exist in memory only.\
> You can plug in any other database backend, and a JSON loader is
> included for quick demos.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

