    -   Log menu: `e` (edit), `x` (delete), `r` (return)
-   ğŸ§© **Log fields**: `ID`, `Name`, `Text`, `Date` (creation timestamp)
-   ğŸ—ï¸ **Clean package boundaries** (`helpers`, `logs`, `database`)
-   ğŸ”Œ **DB-agnostic design** --- any backend implementing the CRUD
    interface works
-   ğŸª¶ **Zero external dependencies** --- pure Go standard library

