### Package Overview

#### **helpers**

Utilities for: - clearing the terminal - reading user input - safe
integer parsing - word-wrapping for long text

#### **logs**

Contains all high-level logic: - list logs - open/view a log - create or
edit a log - delete log entries - orchestrates CLI menu interactions

#### **database**

A simple in-memory implementation: - `map[uint64]Log` storage - CRUD
helpers - JSON import for loading demo data

You can drop in PostgreSQL, SQLite, Redis, BoltDB, etc., by implementing
the same interface.

